# Force LF line endings on text files so the `dist/index.js` freshness
# gate in .github/workflows/release.yml doesn't false-positive on a
# maintainer who clones on Windows with `core.autocrlf=true`. The bundle
# is rebuilt + committed as part of every PR; a CRLF roundtrip would
# silently dirty the file even when the content is identical.
* text=auto eol=lf
dist/** text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.ts text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
